OL,3,CRecycling firm fined #1.2m after
OL,4,Cworker hit by skip wagon
OL,6,FA metals recycling company has been
OL,7,Ffined #1.2m after a worker was hit by
OL,8,Fa 32-tonne skip wagon at a processing
OL,9,Fsite.
OL,11,FThe man was not wearing his high-
OL,12,Fvisibility jacket when he was hit by
OL,13,Fthe vehicle at CF Booth Limited, in
OL,14,FRotherham, on 10 August 2020.
OL,16,FHe suffered a fractured skull and
OL,17,Fcollar bone but has since made a full
OL,18,Frecovery.
