OL,6,FThe Health and Safety Executive said
OL,7,Fthe wagon driver did not see him as he
OL,8,Fcrossed the yard.
OL,10,FIts investigation found the site was
OL,11,Fnot organised to allow pedestrians and
OL,12,Fvehicles to move around safely.
OL,14,FThere was no adequate transport risk
OL,15,Fassessment in place.
